me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.drive

Class MeccanumDrive.MeccanumDriveBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.drive.MeccanumDrive.MeccanumDriveBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    MeccanumDrive

    public static class MeccanumDrive.MeccanumDriveBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder/helper class to simplify the creation of an instance of a MeccanumDrive.

    There are several parameters that you can customize:

    • Front right motor
    • Front left motor
    • Back right motor
    • Back left motor
    • Should X and Y be swapped?
    • Should X be inverted?
    • Should Y be inverted?
    • The kinematics' minimum magnitude
    • The kinematics' maximum magnitude
    • The kinematics' turn magnitude
    • The kinematics' angle offset
